job.title: NIPER Teaching and Non-Teaching Recruitment 2021  Apply online for Various Vacancies in West Bengal
job.body:
Total vacancies:09

Name of the Posts:

  • Technical Asst, System Engineer & Other

Description

New West Bengal Government Jobs have been published by The National Institute of Pharmaceutical Education & Research for the vacancies of System Engineer. If you are finding a government job in West Bengal then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for these vacancies in West Bengal, from 12.05.2021, and till 11.06.2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in West Bengal and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.


Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • No information about application fee

Educational qualification to apply for NIPER System Engineer vacancies in West Bengal:

  • To apply for a System Engineer posts in West Bengal, your Senior Secondary (10+2), Under Graduate, Posts Graduate, MBBS must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is the 12.05.2021
  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 11.06.2021

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 40 years old. 

NIPER System Engineer Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the West Bengal Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is as per norms

How to apply for NIPER Teaching and Non-Teaching Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process for these vacancies in West Bengal. Fill in your details and submit it

  • Or follow all the steps given below,
  •  First, go to the official website of NIPER and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked BY NIPER
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.
